OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FA 65-year-old man has gone on trial
OL,7,Faccused of murdering a former biology
OL,8,Fteacher and dumping his body by a
OL,9,Froadside in Nothumberland.
OL,11,FPaul Black, from Edinburgh, is accused
OL,12,Fof killing 75-year-old Peter Coshan in
OL,13,Fhis flat in Leith in August 2022.
OL,15,FBlack denies murder and a string of
OL,16,Fother charges.
