OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FEdinburgh's High Court heard that
OL,7,FBlack had made contact with Mr Coshan
OL,8,Fon the dating site Gaydar and
OL,9,Fmessaging service Whatsapp and lured
OL,10,Fhim to a property at Fettes College,
OL,11,Fon Seafield Road, in Edinburgh, where
OL,12,Fit is alleged the murder took place.
OL,14,FIt is alleged he then hid the body in
OL,15,Fthe Edinburgh area for a number of
OL,16,Fdays before putting it into a suitcase
OL,17,Fand driving to a layby on the A696
OL,18,Fbetween Otterburn and Belsay, in
OL,19,FNorthumberland.
