OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FThe court heard that, after attempting
OL,7,Fto dig a grave, Black dumped the body
OL,8,Fby a wall and disposed of the
OL,9,Fsuitcase, as well as attempting to
OL,10,Fdispose of clothing and items
OL,11,Fbelonging to Mr Coshan.
OL,13,FMr Coshan's car had last been spotted
OL,14,Fin the Scottish Borders.
