OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FReading from a joint minute of
OL,7,Fagreement, advocate depute John Keenan
OL,8,FKC told the court that Mr Coshan, who
OL,9,Fhad Parkinson's disease, had called a
OL,10,Ftaxi to take him to the Seafield Road
OL,11,Faddress at around 11.30pm on August 11
OL,12,F2022 and arrived there shortly before
OL,13,Fmidnight.
OL,15,FHe said two of Mr Coshan's friends,
OL,16,Fwho had worked at Fettes College,
OL,17,Fcontacted police after becoming
OL,18,Fconcerned that he had stopped
OL,19,Fresponding to their messages.
