OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FMr Keenan said their suspicions grew
OL,7,Fwhen they received a reply from Mr
OL,8,FCoshan at around 6am on 13 August,
OL,9,Freading: "Sorry phone been playing up
OL,10,Fgetting fixed Tom."
OL,12,FMr Keenan described this message as
OL,13,F"out of character" for Mr Coshan, who
OL,14,Fused correct grammar and did not use
OL,15,Fabbreviations like "Tom" (meaning
OL,16,F"tomorrow"). His friends suspected
OL,17,Fthat the WhatsApp message "had not
OL,18,Fbeen written by Peter".
