OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FThe court was told that in the days
OL,7,Ffollowing the killing, Black made a
OL,8,Fnumber of cash withdrawals from Mr
OL,9,FCoshan's bank account and used his
OL,10,Fbank cards to make purchases including
OL,11,Fan #860 Tag Heuer watch and #4,300
OL,12,Fworth of euros from Ramsdens
OL,13,Fpawnbrokers in Leith on the morning of
OL,14,F12 August.
