OL,3,CBody of man was 'put into suitcase and
OL,4,Cdumped at roadside', murder trial hears
OL,6,FThe court heard that the following
OL,7,Fday, Black had used Mr Coshan's cards
OL,8,Fto take out two car insurance policies
OL,9,F- one being for the Vauxhall Vectra
OL,10,Fwhich it is alleged he used to
OL,11,Ftransport Mr Coshan's body to
OL,12,FNorthumberland.
OL,14,FPaul Black has pleaded not guilty to
OL,15,F18 charges.
OL,17,FThe trial continues.
